==Translingual==
===Etymology===
based on the [[generic name]] ''[[Helianthus]]'' (Art 19 ''[[ICBN]]'')

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Heliantheae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[tribe]], within [[family]] ''Compositae'' (aka ''[[Asteraceae]]''). Circumscription of the tribe will vary with [[taxonomic]] viewpoint. 

